ce of the predicted $G_{vrh}$ across multiple forward passes with slightly jittered input features to quantify the model\'s confidence in the "mechanical viability" of metastable phases.\n\n6. **Simplify Validation**: The "leave-one-metal-out" check in Step 8 is computationally expensive if done for all candidates. Focus this check specifically on the top 10 candidates identified in Step 7 to keep the workflow efficient.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='3c3fb264-a86a-46ec-896e-eb6f992ac839'



