han just prediction. Specifically, check if the model\'s predicted $G_{vrh}$ for metastable phases follows the expected physical trend: $G_{vrh}$ should generally decrease as `energy_above_hull` increases (the "softening" effect). If the model predicts high $G_{vrh}$ for highly unstable materials, it may be overfitting to structural proxies.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='b878cf3a-641c-4f49-ad33-913cec80a259'



